            "body": "thanks for the ping!\r\ni just realized that reloading a loaded module without letting it get a chance to react can cause unknown impacts, and sometimes it harms and leaks.\r\n\r\nto handle this, IMO it needs additional specifics to define a module,\r\nsay the module provides a destruction, or subscribes to a particular event, or whatever,\r\nnone is what i want to see definitely.\r\n\r\nso i think this need is just too bad to have, even it's for debugging/developing stage.\r\n",
